headline.print_headline: Ukraine Crowds Want Yanukovich Out Despite Political Deal
headline.main: Ukraine Crowds Want Yanukovich Out Despite Political Deal

lead_paragraph: Emotional crowds on Kiev's Independence Square rounded on opposition leaders on Friday after they signed an agreement with President Viktor Yanukovich to end a protracted crisis, and said they would not wait any longer for him to go.
